    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Morphological characters of Lysmata ternatensis De Man, 1902 from Agatti Island, Lakshadweep, India:A—Carapace: 1—Third maxilliped, 2—Upper nntenular flagellum; B—Abdomenal segments; C—dorsal view of rostrum and antennal scale (1); D—first pereopod; E—second pereopod: F—third pereopod; G—Chela of 2nd pereopod; H—Dectylus of third pereopod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3264578/files/figure.png" ;
